希里安·墨菲差点在 2014 年的电视剧中扮演奥本海默https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-nearly-played-oppenheimer-in-a-2014-tv-series-3475708?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=cillian-murphy-nearly-played-奥本海默 2014 年电视剧Sam WarnerMon, 31 Jul 2023 14:02:50 +0000 Film NewsNewsTV News https://www.nme.com/?p=3475708 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>这位明星差点出现在电视剧“曼哈顿”中</p><p>希里安<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-nearly-played-oppenheimer-in-a-2014-tv-series-3475708">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 差点在 2014 年电视剧中扮演奥本海默 (Oppenheimer) 的形象</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="奥本海默" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer_Cillian_Murphy-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>近十年前，<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cillian-murphy">希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy)</a>曾在一部电视剧中饰演 J·罗伯特·奥本海默 (J. Robert Oppenheimer)，这一消息已经浮出水面。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多：<a href="https://www.nme.com/features/film-interviews/cillian-murphy-interview-oppenheimer-3470442">希里安·墨菲谈成为奥本海默：“我出去得不多——我没有社交”</a></strong></li></ul><p>这位明星目前在<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰</a>的电影<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>《奥本海默</em></a>》中饰演被称为“原子弹之父”的理论物理学家。</p><p>然而，2014 年至 2015 年间在 WGN 播出的电视剧<em>《曼哈顿》</em>的创作者公开了该剧的选角过程，透露了在丹尼尔·伦敦最终被选角之前考虑扮演奥本海默的一些演员。</p><p>剧集主管山姆·肖 (Sam Shaw) 告诉<a href="https://www.vanityfair.com/hollywood/2023/07/oppenheimer-manhattan-series-atomic-bomb" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《名利场》杂志</em></a>：“千分百，希里安·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 就在这个名单上。”同时他还透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/series/the-bear"><em>《熊</em></a>》中的埃邦·莫斯-巴克拉赫 (Ebon Moss-Bachrach) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/beck">贝克</a>也曾被考虑出演该角色。 </p><figure id="attachment_3440783" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3440783" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3440783" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg" alt="奥本海默" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/05/Oppenheimer-trailer-cillian-murphy-new-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3440783" class="wp-caption-text"> 《奥本海默》中的希里安·墨菲。图片来源：YouTube</figcaption></figure><p><em>奥本海默</em>是墨菲在诺兰电影中的第一个主要角色，过去曾多次与导演合作出演配角。</p><p>这位演员最近接受了<em>《NME》</em>采访，谈论了出演这个角色的事情，并解释了导演如何用“令人惊叹的短语<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-reveals-how-christopher-nolan-helped-him-unlock-oppenheimer-3472513">”帮助他“解锁”这个角色</a>。</p><p> “克里斯用了这个令人惊奇的短语。我们正在谈论奥本海默的弧线，他说，“你知道，他在道德上在雨滴之间跳舞。”当我准备的时候，这让我的脑海中浮现出一些东西，”他回忆道。</p><p>墨菲进一步解释了奥本海默：“我确实认为他相信这将是结束所有战争的武器。他认为[拥有原子弹]将激励各国形成某种核世界治理。他很天真。” </p><figure id="attachment_3474889" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3474889" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3474889" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie.jpg" alt="奥本海默" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/Oppenheimer-benny-safdie-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3474889" class="wp-caption-text"> 《奥本海默》中的本尼·萨夫迪和希里安·墨菲。图片来源：环球影业</figcaption></figure><p>除了墨菲， <em>《奥本海默》</em>的主演还有艾米莉·布朗特、马特·达蒙、小罗伯特·唐尼、弗洛伦斯·皮尤、乔什·哈奈特、卡西·阿弗莱克、拉米·马雷克和肯尼思·布拉纳。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em>在对<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">该片的五星级评论</a>中表示：“<em>奥本海默</em>不仅是对原子弹背后的人的权威描述，也是成人电影制作领域的一项里程碑式的成就。</p><p> “多年来，诺兰一直在完善严肃大片的艺术——制作巧妙、精心调整、引人注目的多厅史诗片；除了在电影院之外，无法不间断、不受干扰地观看这些内容。但不知何故，这感觉更大。”</p><p>希里安<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/cillian-murphy-nearly-played-oppenheimer-in-a-2014-tv-series-3475708">·墨菲 (Cillian Murphy) 差点在 2014 年电视剧中扮演奥本海默 (Oppenheimer) 的形象</a>首次出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
 “我的世界”模组漏洞使玩家的电脑无法抵御黑客攻击https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/minecraft-mod-vulnerability-leaves-players-pcs-defenceless-against-hackers-3475701?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=minecraft-mod-vulnerability-leaves-玩家电脑无防御能力对抗黑客Imogen DonovanMon, 31 Jul 2023 13:52:23 +0000 Gaming NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3475701 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> “他们实际上可以在目标系统上执行他们想要的任何代码”</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/minecraft-mod-vulnerability-leaves-players-pcs-defenceless-against-hackers-3475701">《我的世界》mod 后的漏洞让玩家的电脑对黑客毫无防御能力，该漏洞</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/games/minecraft"><em>《我的世界》</em></a>玩家被警告称，许多改装服务器存在重大漏洞，导致他们的计算机无法抵御黑客攻击。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/game-reviews/minecraft-legends-review-3429887">《我的世界传奇》评论：即使不总是扣人心弦，但也很迷人</a></strong></li></ul><p>据<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/news/minecraft-bleedingpipe-security-hole-executes-remote-code" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Tom&#39;s Hardware</em></a>报道， <em>《我的世界》</em>恶意软件预防联盟 (MMPA) 在周末向玩家通报了这一发现。 “BleedingPipe 是一种在野外使用的漏洞，允许在 1.7.10/1.12.2 Forge 上运行流行的 Minecraft mods 的客户端和服务器上完全远程执行代码，”该团队<a href="https://blog.mmpa.info/posts/bleeding-pipe/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">解释道</a>。</p><p>他们补充说，可能有更多版本的<em>Minecraft</em>可能面临被利用的风险，并建议玩家认真对待这一警告。 BleedingPipe 的第一个实例出现于去年 3 月，但 MMPA 表示“ <em>Minecraft</em>社区中还没有出现过如此规模的实例”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3475728" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3475728" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3475728" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/minecraft-mods-leave-computers-open-to-malware-attacks-2-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3475728" class="wp-caption-text"> 《我的世界》来源：Mojang Studios</figcaption></figure><p>为了保护人们的计算机和笔记本电脑， <a href="https://github.com/dogboy21/serializationisbad" target="_blank" rel="noopener">GitHub 上的 Dogboy21</a>在许多其他开发人员的帮助下创建了一个修补程序，可以解决所有已知受影响 mod 中的潜在漏洞。</p><p> Dogboy21 表示：“虽然针对此漏洞的攻击数量相对较少，但由于该漏洞的重要性，目前使用未修补的模组是完全危险的。”</p><p> “攻击者已经尝试（在某些情况下成功）窃取 Microsoft 访问令牌和浏览器会话。但由于他们实际上可以在目标系统上执行他们想要的任何代码，因此可能性是无限的，”他们继续说道。</p><p>目前，有越来越多的受影响模组可供玩家参考。 Dogboy21 和其他开发人员指出，他们无法给出 mod 的“确切版本范围”，并且由于持续努力识别漏洞，该列表并不完整。</p><p>在其他游戏新闻中， <em><a href="https://www.nme.com/games/super-smash-bros">《任天堂明星大乱斗》的</a></em>创作者樱井正宏表示，<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/nintendo">任天堂</a>没有人能够<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/super-smash-bros-creator-cant-really-imagine-new-game-being-made-without-him-3475677">“简单地掌控”</a>该系列的发展方向。</p><p> <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/minecraft-mod-vulnerability-leaves-players-pcs-defenceless-against-hackers-3475701">《我的世界》mod 后的漏洞让玩家的电脑对黑客毫无防御能力，该漏洞</a>首先出现在<a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
