uploads/2023/07/Rotten-Tomatoes-web-page-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>烂番茄上粉丝评分最高的电影出炉了。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/oppenheimer-review-christopher-nolan-3470392">《奥本海默》评论：克里斯托弗·诺兰令人兴奋的传记片像一颗炸弹一样击中大脑</a></strong></li></ul><p>这个评论聚合网站早在 1998 年就推出了，最近深入研究了<a href="https://editorial.rottentomatoes.com/article/the-biggest-and-best-movies-of-the-last-25-years/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一些最大的里程碑，</a>以纪念上线 25 周年。</p><p>其中收视率最高的影片是2008年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/batman">蝙蝠侠</a>电影<em>《黑暗骑士》，</em>新鲜度高达94%，收视率超过50万。</p><p>烂番茄称<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/christopher-nolan">克里斯托弗·诺兰的</a>电影为“持久的文化试金石”，该片见证了克里斯蒂安·贝尔饰演的斗篷十字军与希斯·莱杰饰演的小丑的对决。 </p><figure id="attachment_3425261" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3425261" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3425261" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main.jpg" alt="黑暗骑士" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/04/Heath-Ledger-Joker-main-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3425261" class="wp-caption-text">希斯·莱杰在《黑暗骑士》中饰演小丑。图片来源：娱乐图片/Alamy</figcaption></figure><p> “这部电影不仅被广泛认为是最好的超级英雄电影之一，而且是有史以来最好的电影之一，句号，94％的番茄评分与其观众评分相匹配，这是评论家和粉丝全心全意同意的一件事， “ 他们说。</p><p>早在一月份，导演史蒂文·斯皮尔伯格就建议<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/the-dark-knight-best-picture-oscar-steven-spielberg-3386516"><em>《黑暗骑士》</em>应该获得奥斯卡最佳影片提名</a>，并表示当<a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avatar-way-of-the-water"><em>《阿凡达：水之道》</em></a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/top-gun-maverick-review-tom-cruise-miles-teller-3224047"><em>《壮志凌云：枪特立独行》</em></a>成为今年早些时候获得提名的第一部大片续集时，他感到很受鼓舞。 。</p><p> “我对此感到非常鼓舞，”他告诉<a href="https://deadline.com/2023/01/oscars-2023-steven-spielberg-the-fabelmans-indiana-jones-disney-series-1235239433/#recipient_hashed=ceda9ce92d353d005479ddc8bee4521d81386c4e04b2f8c173868b6f2a857ee3&amp;recipient_salt=d3d49b6fee1be9a42a674414115402c860effaccf064ef72bdf4aa865b99e708"><em>Deadline</em></a> 。 “[But] it came late for the film that should have been nominated a number of years ago, Christopher Nolan&#39;s <em>The Dark Knight</em> .</p><p> “That movie would have definitely garnered a Best Picture Nomination today, so having these two blockbusters solidly presented on the top 10 list is something we should all be celebrating.” </p><figure id="attachment_2681162" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-2681162" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-2681162" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight.jpg" alt="黑暗骑士" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/06/The_Dark_Knight-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-2681162" class="wp-caption-text"> Christian Bale played Batman with a seriousness that hadn&#39;t been seen before. Credit: Warner Bros.</figcaption></figure><p> The film did earn eight Oscar nominations back in 2009, with Ledger winning posthumously in the Best Supporting Actor category.</p><p> Nolan&#39;s latest film <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/oppenheimer"><em>Oppenheimer</em></a> was recently released in cinemas, and stars Cillian Murphy (who played the villain Scarecrow in <em>The Dark Knight</em> trilogy) as the titular J. Robert Oppenheimer.</p><p> Murphy originally auditioned for the role of Batman, and Nolan recently <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/christopher-nolan-reflects-on-decision-not-to-cast-cillian-murphy-as-batman-3441812">spoke about his decision not to cast the actor</a> in the heroic role.</p><p> “Everybody was so excited by watching you perform that when I then said to them, &#39;Okay, Christian Bale is Batman, but what about Cillian to play Scarecrow?&#39; there was no dissent,” he told <a href="https://ew.com/movies/oppenheimer-christopher-nolan-cillian-murphy-in-conversation/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>Entertainment Weekly</em></a> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/this-is-the-highest-rated-film-on-rotten-tomatoes-by-fans-3475644">This is the highest fan-rated film on Rotten Tomatoes</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
